Class GenericController

  • java.lang.Object
    • control.GenericController
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddTagController, CaptionController, CopyController, DeleteTagController, DisplayController, MoveController

    public abstract class GenericController
extends java.lang.Object
    GenericController is an abstract class which sets up the generic structure found in all controllers called by the AlbumController class
    Author:
    Niles Ball, Scott Lahart
